  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>plant based</strong> <strong>'Nduja </strong>(save the rest for later!) and<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until golden, stirring frequently</p><p>Once the breadcrumbs are golden, transfer them to a bowl and reserve the pan – this is your <strong>plant based</strong> <strong>'Nduja pangrattato</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Deseed your <strong>sweet pointed pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 7-9 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked linguine</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>and <strong>sliced pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-6 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, add the <strong>remaining plant based</strong> <strong>'Nduja</strong> and your <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>with 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained linguine </strong>and your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>with a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato & pepper linguine</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/tomato-linguine-with-plant-based-nduja-pangrattato/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>tomato & pepper linguine </strong>and sprinkle the<strong> plant based 'Nduja pangrattato </strong>over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
